<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-black dark:text-white p-3 md:p-6 transition-colors duration-300"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Info Box -->
  <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 p-4 md:p-6 pb-8 rounded-lg">
    <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold">•</span>
        <span>I verbi <strong>dovere, potere e volere</strong> sono chiamati <strong class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">verbi servili</strong> perché possono accompagnare un altro verbo (coniugato all'infinito) e formare con esso un unico predicato verbale → <em>Devo comprare</em> (predicato verbale) <em>un giubbotto.</em> → <em>Vuoi provare</em> (predicato verbale) <em>il mio?</em></span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 font-bold">•</span>
        <span>Dovere, potere e volere possono anche essere usati da soli, con un <strong class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">significato proprio</strong> → <em>Paola vuole</em> (predicato verbale) <em>un gelato con la panna.</em></span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
  <div class="p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="multiple-choice">
    <h2 class="font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
      Scrivi S se il verbo evidenziato è usato come servile, P se è usato con significato proprio.
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <strong>Vuoi</strong> fare i compiti con loro?</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_1" value="S" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">S</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_1" value="P" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">P</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Isa <strong>può</strong> restare a cena da noi?</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_2" value="S" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">S</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_2" value="P" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">P</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Ti <strong>devo</strong> prestare quel romanzo.</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_3" value="S" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">S</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_3" value="P" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">P</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Max <strong>vuole</strong> un'altra fetta di torta.</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_4" value="S" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">S</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_4" value="P" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">P</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Mi <strong>devi</strong> un favore!</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_5" value="S" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">S</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_5" value="P" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">P</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Non <strong>potete</strong> dire queste bugie.</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_6" value="S" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">S</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_6" value="P" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">P</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 2: Complete with servili -->
  <div class="p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
      Completa con le forme dei verbi servili adatte.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Il sole è accecante e</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-28 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="devo" data-correct-answer="devo">
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">indossare gli occhiali.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Corro!</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-28 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="Devo" data-correct-answer="Devo">
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">essere a casa alle tre.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Se</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-28 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="vuoi" data-correct-answer="vuoi">
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">giocare, prima</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-28 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="devi" data-correct-answer="devi">
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">finire i compiti.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Voi</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-28 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="potete" data-correct-answer="potete">
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">prestarmi una penna?</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Sofia non</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-28 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="può" data-correct-answer="può">
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">venire con noi.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Luca</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-28 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="deve" data-correct-answer="deve">
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">allenarsi molto se</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-28 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="vuole" data-correct-answer="vuole">
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">battere il record.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 3 -->
  <div class="p-4 md:p-6 pb-8">
    <h2 class="font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">3</span>
      Scrivi sul quaderno una frase con ciascuno dei seguenti verbi accompagnandoli con un verbo servile.
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-3 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
        regalare
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-3 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
        correre
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-3 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
        inviare
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-3 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
        prendere
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
</div>
